sentences.sentence: I have Whitetail very close to me and move back to the jeep.
sentences.translation: 我把白尾巴拉近了十点儿，退向吉普车。

sentences.sentence: Around the next bend, a whitetail deer saw me and backed off through the cattails.
sentences.translation: 大约在明年弯曲，一白尾鹿看到我后退了通过香蒲。

sentences.sentence: I get out of the jeep with Dog and Whitetail, and lots of children run up to see who I am.
sentences.translation: 我和狗狗、白尾巴下了吉普车，很多小孩儿跑过来看我是谁。
